        <section id="sectors">

            <h2>Our Divisions</h2>

            <ul class="sectors-list">

                <li><strong>Mergers & Acquisitions (M&A):</strong> Researching and analyzing key trends in M&A activity across industries.</li>

                <li><strong>Equity Research:</strong> Providing in-depth analysis of equity markets, stock trends, and company performance.</li>

                <li><strong>Debt Markets:</strong> Exploring developments in bond markets, interest rates, and credit analysis.</li>

                <li><strong>Macroeconomics:</strong> Studying global economic trends, policy impacts, and market implications.</li>

                <li><strong>Sustainable Finance:</strong> Evaluating ESG investments, green bonds, and corporate sustainability practices.</li>

                <li><strong>Technology and FinTech:</strong> Analyzing disruptive technologies and their impact on the financial sector.</li>

            </ul>

        </section>



